# @node-versions: v25.9.0,v26.x
# @description: Flip V8's temporal_rs include path to socket-btm shim
#
# V8's js-temporal-objects.cc #includes `temporal_rs/*.hpp`, which
# upstream resolves through a header set shipped by the Rust crate
# `temporal_capi` at deps/crates/vendor/temporal_capi/bindings/cpp/.
# Building those headers requires rustc + cargo + ICU4X data crates
# (~50 transitive deps, ~5 minute cold build).
#
# socket-btm ships a hand-written C++ port of temporal_capi (the
# `temporal-infra` package) plus a drop-in shim layer at
# packages/temporal-infra/include/temporal_rs/ that has the same
# `temporal_rs::*` surface V8 expects but routes everything to the
# C++ port instead of through diplomat/FFI to Rust.
#
# Two changes:
#
# 1. In deps/crates/crates.gyp:
#    - Drop the `temporal_capi` target's `dependencies: [node_crates]`
#      so building it no longer triggers `cargo build`.
#    - Repoint `direct_dependent_settings.include_dirs` from
#      `<(cargo_vendor_dir)/temporal_capi/bindings/cpp` to `../../include`
#      (relative to deps/crates/crates.gyp = the Node source root's
#      include/, populated by copy-additions.mts from
#      packages/temporal-infra/include/temporal_rs/ via the additions
#      pipeline in prepare-external-sources.mts).
#
# Result: V8 still depends on `:temporal_capi` (so the include path
# still applies), but resolving that target is now a no-op — no rustc,
# no cargo, no ICU4X data crates. Verified `:node_crates` has no other
# gyp consumers, so dropping the dependency removes the Rust build
# entirely. The rustc/cargo toolchain in the Docker images and
# build-toolchain setup can be removed in a follow-up commit once a
# successful smol build proves the shim is correct.
#
# Files modified:
# - deps/crates/crates.gyp: temporal_capi target points at our shim
#
--- a/deps/crates/crates.gyp
+++ b/deps/crates/crates.gyp
@@ -114,12 +114,9 @@
       'target_name': 'temporal_capi',
       'type': 'none',
       'toolsets': ['host', 'target'],
       'sources': [],
-      'dependencies': [
-        'node_crates',
-      ],
       'direct_dependent_settings': {
         'include_dirs': [
-          '<(cargo_vendor_dir)/temporal_capi/bindings/cpp',
+          '../../include',
         ],
       },
     },
